Package grafioschtrader.gtnet.handler.impl

Class LastpriceExchangeHandler

java.lang.Object
grafioschtrader.gtnet.handler.AbstractGTNetMessageHandler
grafioschtrader.gtnet.handler.impl.LastpriceExchangeHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
GTNetMessageHandler
@Component public class LastpriceExchangeHandler extends AbstractGTNetMessageHandler
Handler for GT_NET_LASTPRICE_EXCHANGE_SEL_C requests from remote instances. Processes intraday price data requests and returns prices that are newer than the requester's timestamps. Delegates to strategy classes based on the local server's acceptRequest mode:
  • PushOpenLastpriceQueryStrategy for AC_PUSH_OPEN: Queries GTNetLastprice* tables (shared price pool)
  • OpenLastpriceQueryStrategy for AC_OPEN: Queries and updates local Security/Currencypair entities
See Also:
